title: Common ft. Pharrell - Universal Mind Control
description:
First cut from the long-awaited, four-time delayed new Common album: "Universal Mind Control", featuring Pharrell of The Neptunes. Sporting a brand new (or unCommon) sound, the song was meant to be released this summer, as a part of Common&#039;s 8th studio album, "Invincible Summer". Thus the "electro-tinged" and "techno-inspired" sound. The album has been pushed and pushed, and final release date is now Dec. 9th. 2008.

The beat is hypnotic like nothing I&#039;ve heard in a while.
Also, insane video by Hype Williams. YouTube it. 

Sorry for the low bitrate. Then again, you&#039;re going to bang this in headphones anyway:)

Bitrate: 128 kps
Length: 3m30s



My first torrent, btw. Sorry for any mistakes.
